  "body": "# Bug Report\r\nFollowup of https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15405\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nIf you focus on the `Type password` field the tips (`Lower case`, `Upper-case`, etc) hide behind the keyboard on iOS devices, so you need to press `Return` to see again what characters are missing.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n`Tips` move up with the keyboard and remain above it when it's expanded \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/227577278-74912850-422f-4658-955c-5a8b74112509.MP4\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Start creating a new account\r\n2. On the `Create profile password` screen tap the `Type password` field\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 28/03\r\n- Operating System: iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
